OL,4,Ccar as a weapon' to murder fiance
OL,6,FWarning - some viewers may find the
OL,7,FCCTV footage distressing
OL,9,FA student who drove at her fiance
OL,10,Fbefore dragging him along a road has
OL,11,Fbeen jailed for a minimum of 18 years
OL,12,Ffor his murder.
OL,14,FAlice Wood, 24, claimed her partner
OL,15,FRyan Watson died in a "tragic
OL,16,Faccident" when he was hit by the Ford
OL,17,FFiesta she was driving near their home
OL,18,Fin Rode Heath, , at about 11.30pm on 6
OL,19,FMay 2022.
