OL,3,CWoman jailed for life for 'using her
OL,4,Ccar as a weapon' to murder fiance
OL,6,FBut she was found guilty of murder at
OL,7,FChester Crown Court in January, where
OL,8,Fshe was sentenced to life on Friday 2
OL,9,FFebruary.
OL,11,FThe three-week trial heard the couple
OL,12,Fhad spent the evening at a party in
OL,13,FHanley, Stoke-on-Trent, with staff and
OL,14,Fservice users of the brain injury
OL,15,Fcharity Headway, where Mr Watson was a
OL,16,Fsupport worker.
OL,18,FThe court heard that Mr Watson had
OL,19,F"clicked" with another woman at the
OL,20,Fparty, angering Wood.
