OL,6,FAndrew Ford KC, prosecuting, said Mr
OL,7,FWatson was seen on CCTV footage
OL,8,F"having a good time, being a
OL,9,Fgregarious and outgoing party guest"
OL,10,Fwhile Wood was described by one woman
OL,11,Fattending as "a bit cold".
OL,13,FFellow party guest Tiffany Ferriday
OL,14,Ftold the court she and Mr Watson had
OL,15,F"clicked" and Wood was "pretty much
OL,16,Fleft out" of conversation.
