OL,6,FDuring his opening address, Mr Ford
OL,7,Fsaid "she lost her temper" and "used
OL,8,Fthe car as a weapon".
OL,10,FThe jury was told Mr Watson was
OL,11,Ftrapped underneath the car as Wood
OL,12,Fdrove 158 metres up Sandbach Road
OL,13,Fbefore stopping.
OL,15,FShe told a nearby resident; 'please
OL,16,Fphone an ambulance, I think I've run
OL,17,Fover my boyfriend'.
OL,19,FEmergency services responded and
OL,20,Fparamedics pronounced Mr Watson dead
OL,21,Fat the scene.
