OL,6,FShe told her GP her boyfriend had died
OL,7,Fthe previous week, having jumped in
OL,8,Ffront of her car, and on the way to
OL,9,Fthe police station admitted 'I deserve
OL,10,Fit.'
OL,12,FThese admissions of guilt, along with
OL,13,Fthe extensive CCTV footage meant the
OL,14,Fevidence stacked up against Woods, and
OL,15,Fthe jury ruled that she was guilty of
OL,16,Fmurder.
OL,18,FDavid Jones, Senior Crown Prosecutor
OL,19,Fin CPS Mersey-Cheshire, said: "This
OL,20,Fwas a tragic loss of life of a young
OL,21,Fman with his whole life ahead of him.
