OL,6,F"Under the influence of alcohol, it
OL,7,Fwas clear that Alice Wood's jealousy
OL,8,Fwas ammunition enough for her to
OL,9,Fbrutally kill her partner."
OL,11,F"Though it will never make up for
OL,12,Ftheir devastating loss, I hope today's
OL,13,Fconviction brings Ryan's family some
OL,14,Fsolace, knowing his murderer has been
OL,15,Fbrought to justice."
